    ># Alex Rivera — Senior Backend Engineer

## Professional Summary
8 years building high-traffic web services. Strongest in Python/Django and
distributed systems. I care about reliability, legible code, and shipping things
that actually work for users.

## Skills
Python, Django, FastAPI, PostgreSQL, Redis, Celery, Docker, Kubernetes,
