## Work History

**Meridian Health** (2021–present) — Lead Backend Engineer
- Redesigned the patient intake API — reduced average response time from 1.2s
  to 180ms by replacing synchronous DB calls with async workers
- Led a team of 3 engineers through a HIPAA compliance audit; zero findings
- Introduced SQLAlchemy to a Django codebase, reducing N+1 query issues by ~70%

**CartPulse** (2018–2021) — Software Engineer
- Built a real-time inventory sync system handling 50k events/minute using Celery + Redis
